"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:154
msgid "Wasted Wind"
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:155
msgid ""
"\n"
"    a data project by Robin Hawkes about wasted wind energy in Great "
"Britain. I am grateful for that work as a model for explaining curtailed "
"renewables in a clear, public-facing way.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:162
msgid "About"
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:164
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I built Wasted Sun as a private individual. It is not an official "
"Octopus Energy product, website, or communication.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:169
msgid ""
"\n"
"    I care a great deal about this topic in part because of my role as "
"Head of Technology at Octopus Energy Spain — but except where stated "
"otherwise, the analysis and opinions here are mine alone and do not "
"represent my employer.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:176
msgid ""
"\n"
"  Figures are derived from Red Eléctrica de España data and processed "
"independently for this site;\n"
"  they are not official REE publications or government statistics.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""

#: wasted_sun/templates/day.html:182
msgid ""
"\n"
"  This is a personal side project by Enrique Tasa and is not endorsed by "
"Octopus Energy.\n"
"  "
msgstr ""

